#    [ ] Add Google Analytics tracking ID (optional)
#    [ ] Add Mixpanel token (optional)
#    [ ] Add Sentry DSN for error tracking (recommended)
#
# 4. Security
#    [ ] Verify GENERATE_SOURCEMAP=false
#    [ ] Verify NODE_ENV=production
#    [ ] Verify debug flags are disabled
#    [ ] Test CORS configuration
